data.description: Welcome to the home on Shone Ave, this 2 bedroom and 1 bathroom is close to the 580 freeway with great views of the Oakland hills. The property needs some TLC such as interior painting and refinishing the hardwood flooring. All the appliances are basically brand new including the washer and dryer. Don't miss out on the chance to turn this house into the home you've wanted.
